messages.messageBody:
andrea Smith wrote:

> My concept was that the battle of Sekigahara happened
> on October 21st, 1600 and not September 15th, 1600,
> other events happened, like the Dutch ship sailing
> into Japanese land.

Well, that's the point.

It *was* October 21. It was, though, also 9/15. Lunar calendar vs. Solar calendar.

Tony
